Version 1 of XML Output Toggling by Textfyre begins here.

Use authorial modesty;

Part 1 - For release

XML Output is a truth state which varies. XML Output is true.

Part 2 - Not for release

XML Toggling is an action out of world applying to nothing.
Understand "xml" as xml toggling.

When play begins:
	change XML Output to false.

Carry out xml toggling:
	if XML Output is false begin;
		change XML output to true;
	otherwise;
		change XML output to false;
	end if;

Report xml toggling:
	say "XML is now turned ";
	if XML Output is false begin;
		say "off.";
	otherwise;
		say "on.";
	end if;

XML Output Toggling ends here.
